- **Eagles offense**: more **11â€‘personnel** and WRâ€‘driven explosives; in highâ€‘leverage downs they lean on **Hurts** (scramble/RZ keeper) and perimeter isolation routes.  
- **Trenches & tempo**: Eaglesâ€™ OL continuity vs. a stillâ€‘gelling KC front; game flow favors **longer KC drives** over explosives if WR depth is thin.  
